    "text": "Inspired by the <https://futureofcoding.org/episodes/061.html|Programming as Theory Building> episode we are building a tool to help development teams capture &amp; store the theory of their program text.\nWe achieve this through auto-generation of logical paths through the codebase which developers explain to each-other through voice and video.\n\nWe would love to hear the thoughts of this community specifically as many of you will see what we are trying to achieve here.\nCheckout out our <https://www.ycombinator.com/launches/KWX-ten-dev-understand-code-remarkably-fast|launch> for more info.",
